### ğŸ” Examples of Local LLMs

| Model                     | Size   | Highlights                            |
| ------------------------- | ------ | ------------------------------------- |
| **LLaMA 3 8B/70B**        | 4â€“70GB | Meta's open models (state-of-the-art) |
| **Mistral 7B**            | 4â€“10GB | Dense & fast, open weights            |
| **Gemma 2B/7B**           | 2â€“7GB  | Google's open models                  |
| **Phi-2 / Phi-3**         | 1.3â€“7B | Small, high-quality for on-device use |
| **TinyLLM / GGML Alpaca** | 1â€“3GB  | Tiny inference models                 |

